Author: Vaultbank.io
Title: Vault Bank ICO
Body: Thank you very much for your kind words about our upcoming ICO! Presale starts December 13th with a 15% bonus, please check out our website for more info.

Author: Vaultbank.io
Title: Vault Bank ICO
Body: Hi Choyer! Please check out our website and whitepaper and all other materials on our website for more information, and also please join our Telegram group t.me/VaultbankICO to ask direction questions to our team. We of course consider the offering phenomenal, mainly as we are offering one of the first ever asset backed tokens that are linked to our company, and the three business lines we are setting up.  1) The Vaultbank Fund - a real secure asset backed portfolio 2) The Vaultbank debit MasterCard - a debit card allowing for crypto usability at MasterCard terminals. This will start for residents of the European Union and the United States after the ICO closes, and we will continue to gain licenses and create partnerships in order to offer our debit cards to residents of other people in the world. 3) The Vaultbank Exchange - a cryptocurrency trading exchange platform that will compete on fees, customer service, and wide usability with security token offerings as well as utility tokens.  Please let me know if you have any questions!

Author: Vaultbank.io
Title: Vault Bank ICO
Body: Thanks so much Lucas. There really are so many ICOs now, and we are doing our best to show why we are unique, as an asset backed security token, that actually means that each token holder owns part of the whole company and all business lines (but without voting rights). We are striving to pay out the first dividends by a cryptocurrency offering, and also offer debit cards that can be linked to various cryptocurrencies, and also an exchange that will offer low fees and wide usability and also great customer service.  Hopefully you are able to participate. Thanks!

Author: Vaultbank.io
Title: Vault Bank ICO
Body: Hi! Please go to Vaultbank.io and click on the SUBSCRIBE button that is part of the Orderbook.io widget that is in our website. That will start the investor verification process, which can take up to 48 hours, so that as soon as our presale opens on December 13th, you can invest right away if you are approved and choose to participate.  Thanks!

Author: Vaultbank.io
Title: Vault Bank ICO
Body: Hi there! We are partnered with a debit card and credit card company based in the United Kingdom that has the relationship with MasterCard, and that is creating the Vaultbank debit MasterCards for us. When the ICO closes, we will be able to distribute cards to residents in the European Union and the United States (up to I believe 20k cards) and those card holders can use them wherever MasterCard is accepted.  We are also working on a license for distributing cards in Asia, and also in parts of Latin America, but those aren't finalized yet. We will continue working on attaining additional licenses as well as partnering with additional companies to offer further distribution around the world.

Author: Vaultbank.io
Title: Vault Bank ICO
Body: Oh this was an exciting thread to see started up. Thank you Reformed Trader for your interest in our upcoming ICO. Reformed trader I don't believe is part of our team, so this is great to see.  We will be making our full announcement of the ICO next week. Until then, please do check out our website for information about Vaultbank and what we are doing. We are proud to be offering Security tokens that are secured asset backed and that will be earning quarterly dividends, and we are also very proud of the Debit card we will be offering that allows for some cryptocurrencies to be used around the world for everyday goods and services, and also an investing and trading terminal with low fees and ease of use.  We have a great team and a great long term business model.  As for any questions about the bounty campaign, information about it will be in the announcement next week.

Be careful with this one guys or please prove me I'm wrong.
